      "bbox": [
        51.599998474121094,
        98.74400329589844,
        561.075927734375,
        130.36398315429688
      ],
      "text": "\uf0b7 \nAs per 3rd Advance Estimates 2025-26, about 116.3 percent of the normal area has been \nsown under the summer season crops. \n",
      "type": "text",
      "source_type": "pdfblock"
    },
    {
      "block_index": 6,
      "page": 8,
      "bbox": [
        51.599998474121094,
        133.0640106201172,
        560.7318115234375,
        164.68399047851562
      ],
      "text": "\uf0b7 \nRice: About 32.63 lakh ha area coverage under Summer Rice has been reported as \ncompared to 33.28 lakh ha during the corresponding period of last year.  \n",
      "type": "text",
      "source_type": "pdfblock"
    },
    {
      "block_index": 7,
      "page": 8,
      "bbox": [
        51.599998474121094,
        167.2639617919922,
        560.9620361328125,
        198.88400268554688
      ],
      "text": "\uf0b7 \nPulses: About 27.16 lakh ha area coverage has been reported compared to 27.07 lakh ha \nduring the corresponding period of last year.  \n",
      "type": "text",
      "source_type": "pdfblock"
    },
    {
      "block_index": 8,
      "page": 8,
      "bbox": [
        51.599998474121094,
        201.58396911621094,
        561.112060546875,
        233.20401000976562
      ],
